title: Introducing: The Psychologists Are In with Maggie Lawson and Timothy Omundson
description:
We would love to introduce you to a podcast  called “The Psychologists Are In” a Psych rewatch podcast hosted by Maggie Lawson and Timothy Omundson. Each week they talk about your favorite episodes from the show, share behind-the-scenes stories, incredible memories, and have drop-in visits from their best friends and fellow cast mates.
